title: Wordle players break streaks to support New York Times union walkout
description: Some Wordle players broke their streaks Thursday to support the New York Times union. Even for a cause, a broken streak can be a tough pill to swallow.

title: Your selfies are helping AI learn. You did not consent to this.
description: What are the rules of the road for the A.I. age, where anything you share online might train a computer system that puts an innocent person in jail?

title: The Magic Avatar you paid $3.99 for is probably stolen, artists say
description: Artists say Lensa's Magic Avatars are built by AI that uses techniques and styles that were taken from artists without consent or compensation.

title: Steve Aoki, Kpop star T.O.P to fly around moon with Japanese billionaire
description: Space enthuasiast and entrepreneur Yusaku Maezawa on Friday announced the eight people who will join him on a trip around the moon.
